# Base4Tone-vim

## Themes for Vim

All colorschemes come in a separate dark and light version.
These themes are tested in Gvim, but when using Vim within terminals which **do not** support truecolor, it will use the converted colors from one theme which are as close as possible in the 8-bit 256 colorspace.

